":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cbf5gm3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCbf5gm3.png&h=7053022b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大把人幫襯"},{"pid":"9ffdb077b71c02dc9098b61a2ca900b25803e9b2","tid":1617301,"uid":8873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:47:56.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"6382c6c9d49314d79bde9a8ce09713190a8e9044","tid":1617301,"uid":259963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zOMHk1N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzOMHk1N.png&h=649b24fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">私了一定要爆春袋</span><br />\n仲要唔致命（左膠大愛）<br />\n<br />\n一路叫唔好打頭一路大大力錫佢春袋<br />\n個畫面正到諗起都想打個飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你諗下如果你係藍絲<br />\n比人私了打爆頭壯烈d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係比人私了爆春袋搞笑d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔通大大聲係記者鏡頭面前話比人爆袋咩？<br />\n有力講都無面講啦"}]}